ost Pub]]'' (1994)\n*''[[Sharaku (film)|Sharaku]]'' (1995)\n*''[[School Ghost Stories]]'' (1995)\n*''[[Moonlight Serenade (1997 film)|Moonlight Serenade]]'' (1997)\n*''[[Wait and See (1998 film)|Wait and See]]'' (1998)\n*''[[Tsuribaka Nisshi Eleven]]'' (2000)\n*''[[New Battles Without Honor and Humanity (2000 film)|New Battles Without Honor and Humanity]]'' (2000)\n*''[[Suicide Club (film)|Suicide Club]]'' (2002)\n*''[[Aiki (film)|Aiki]]'' (2002)\n*''[[Caf\u00e9 Lumi\u00e8re]]'' (2003)\n*''[[Drugstore Girl]]'' (2004)\n*''[[Tokyo Tower (film)|Tokyo Tower]]'' (2005)\n*''[[Break Through!]]'' (2005)\n*''[[Yamato (film)|Yamato]]'' (2005)\n*''[[Virgin Snow (film)|Virgin Snow]]'' (2007)\n*''[[The Ramen Girl]]'' (2008)\n*''[[Departures (2008 film)|Departures]]'' (2008)\n*''[[Air Doll]]'' (2009)\n*''[[Dear Doctor (film)|Dear Doctor]]'' (2009)\n*''[[Villain (2010 film)|Villain]]'' (2010)\n*''[[The Lone Scalpel]]'' (2010)\n*''[[Rebirth (2011 film)|Rebirth]]'' (2011)\n*''[[Hoshi Mamoru Inu]]'' (2011)\n*''[[Tsure ga Utsu ni Narimashite]]'' (2011)\n*''[[Dirty Hearts]]'' (2011)\n*''[[Bread of Happiness]]'' (2012)\n*''[[Ace Attorney (film)|Ace Attorney]]'' (2012)\n*''[[Gaiji Keisatsu]]'' (2012)\n*''[[Ai to Makoto]]'' (2012)\n*''[[Anata e]]'' (2012)\n*''[[Shield of Straw]]'' (2013)\n*''[[A Story of Yonosuke]]'' (2013)\n*''[[Parasyte: Part 1]]'' (2014)\n*''[[Shinya Shokud\u014d]]'' (2015)\n*''[[Tsukuroi Tatsu Hito (film)|Tsukuroi Tatsu Hito]]'' (2015)\n*''[[Shin Godzilla]]'' (2016)\n*''[[Black Widow Business]]'' (2016)\n*''[[Midnight Diner: Tokyo Stories]]'' (2016)\n*''Perfect Revolution'' (2017)\n*''Ringside Story'' (2017)\n*''Kage ni Dakarete Nemure'' (2019)\n*''Tell Me the Way to the Station'' (2019)\n*''AI Amok'' (2020)\n*''Step'' (2020)\n*''Red'' (2020)\n*''Naku-Ko wa Inega'' (2020)\n\n===Television===\n*''[[Atsuhime (drama)|Atsuhime]]'' (2008), Fusahime\n*''[[Hanbun, Aoi]]'' (2018), Kimika Okada\n*''Innocent Days'' (2018)\n*''[[The Murder of Roger Ackroyd|Kuroido Goroshi]]'' (2